  A new tag of the whole geometry category is in place. It is called 

     geometry-V00-01-01

and it includes all the new code except the Voxel drawer.  That will be
included in a sub-category tag called   "geommng-V00-01-02".

  It includes the following sub-tags:

   geomsolids-V00-01-03
      [ geom-solids-csg-01-00-02-cand
        geom-solid-bool-V00-01-03b
        breps-V00-01-00
        stepinterface-V00-01-00 ]

   geomvol-01-01-01b

   geommng-V00-01-01

   field-V00-01-02    
